<h1 style="text-align:center">Welcome to App Manager</h1>
<hr>
<br>
<p>
App Manager is an app created to submit, view, and manage job applications for potential future employees. Click the 'Create Application' link below to submit a job application. 
</p>
<br>
<br>
<% if flash[:notice] %>
  <p style="color:blue"> Your application has been submitted for review. Thank you for using the App Manager Web Application. </p>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to 'Create Application', controller: 'job_applications', action: 'new' %>
<% end %>
<br>
<br>
<p>
Administrator options can be reached by first signing in via the "Sign in" link located at the top of the page.
</p>
<br>
<% if signed_in? %>
  <%= link_to 'View Applications (Admin Only)', controller: 'job_applications' %>
<% end %>
